translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_AGREE: Yes, I have read and expressly agree to the <2>Privacy Policy</2> including the Privacy Notice attached below, the <2>Terms of Use</2> and the <2>Terms of Service</2>.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_CONTENT: For the Psychological Numerology Calculator service we use Heroku hosting server. Heroku is a subsidiary of salesforce.com (USA). Heroku stores server log files when used. When you register for the calculator, your email address is stored for account creation at Heroku. You will receive a confirmation email from us with a link that you must click to complete the registration (double-opt in). This ensures that no one else but you uses your email address for account creation. Your data entered in the course of use such as first name, last name, date of birth will also be stored in your account on Heroku. All this happens only as long as you actively use the service and do not delete your account yourself. After 2 years of inactivity, your account and all the data you entered will be automatically deleted. To avoid unintentional deletion, you will receive a notice email from us about this before deletion. This processing is carried out in accordance with Art. 6 para. 1 lit. b DSGVO for the contractual performance of our service.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_CONTENT_2: You may enter the above personal data of other people into the Psychological Numerology Calculator only if you have obtained their express consent beforehand.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_CONTENT_3: The servers and databases provided by Heroku are located in Germany/Europe and are subject to European data protection regulations. In the event that personal data is transferred to the USA, Heroku and Salesforce have submitted to the EU-US Privacy Shield.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_CONTENT_4: The web pages of the Psychological Numerology Calculator use the functions of the web analysis service Google Analytics of Google LLC (USA). In doing so, your IP is recorded exclusively with the extension _anonymizeIp(), which ensures anonymization of the IP address by shortening it and excludes direct personal reference. Only in exceptional cases will the full IP address be transferred to a Google server in the USA and shortened there, whereby Google has submitted to the EU-US Privacy Shield. In these exceptional cases, this processing is carried out in accordance with Art. 6 para. 1 lit. f DSGVO.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_MORE_INFOS: For more information, please see our <2>Privacy Policy.</2>
